	]a
	" improves on 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/TASEditor 
		"TASEditor
	]a
	"'s 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=previous efforts|href=/2652M)
	" by four seconds due to a recently discovered encounter glitch. See the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=author's comments|href=/4371S)
	" for more details.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"We also have 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=a run|href=/3256M)
	" that completes the six palaces without using the Left + Right glitch to turn the game into a barely comprehensible mess (but does allow the use of glitched warps) and 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=another run|href=/3254M)
	" that disallows both the Left + Right glitch and the use of glitched warps.
	$LF
